"nur für Online-Banking-Funktionen benötigt."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating an Account"
msgstr "Anlegen eines Kontos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:176
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You must have a file open before you can create a new account. If you do "
#| "not have an existing file, you will need to <link linkend="
